Author: __blackcoffee
Text: Ugh that's the worst. Yesterday was my worst day, felt so bloated and took a bunch of Midol. I also forgot that Midol helps with water retention and I had to pee ALL DAY but at least the bloat went down. I feel like I can't "judge" what a week off from the gym and eating normally did to my body until this is over.

Text: Oh, I'm on the fourth day of my period and so bloated, cramping hard. I'm spending the day on bed, not eating at all.
